{"tid":671343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青年攜電動板車跳橋死","createTime":"2018-05-20T05:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T06:11:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e98e16b926a688e62a425008f1accf77ff2f229c","tid":671343,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T05:13:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180520/20396220\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180520%2F20396220&d=m2sT9J4EWVKnSDdTd08woJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=2b892977\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180520%2F20396220&h=f2eb74e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180520/20396220</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月20日 <br />\n<br />\n青年攜電動板車跳橋死<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180520/large/20la5p7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180520%2Flarge%2F20la5p7.jpg&h=c473abf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■跳橋身亡青年屍體移送至殮房。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】21歲青年懷疑因工作與前途問題感到失意，昨日凌晨攜同電動滑板車到青衣南橋，未幾於橋面躍下26米墮地重創昏迷，經送院後證實不治，警方調查後相信事件無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾被父斥態度懶散<br />\n<br />\n跳橋身亡青年姓黃，21歲，與家人同住於沙田水泉澳邨。據悉，黃父從事洗衣業生意，他近年到父親的洗衣工場幫手，惟近日曾經被父親責備工作態度懶散，事主顯得鬱鬱寡歡。於前晚深夜時分，有途人目擊黃站於青衣南橋上，身旁放有電動滑板車，倚着欄杆悶悶不樂，但途人未有為意。<br />\n<br />\n至昨日凌晨零時許，黃被發現倒卧橋下26米深的長輝路地面，報警送院搶救，惟一小時後證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n警方在現場未有發現遺書，其後聯絡家人到醫院認屍，初步獲悉死者早前曾經與父親因為工作及前途問題發生爭執，雙方事後雖然言歸於好，惟事主於深夜攜電動滑板車離家尋死，家人聞噩耗後傷心不已。警方調查後相信事件無可疑，死因交法醫檢驗確認。<br />\n<br />\n■記者江寶龍  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n抹窗失重心　女子墮樓亡<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n拆遷前最幸福的相遇　新界東北遺民救末期癌浪浪"},{"pid":"a11aba63ff3b3cc513dd347349fad1de8e8467cd","tid":671343,"uid":88428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T05:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c9d75d71277fd33d35c6b03367f7fb45c5b905","tid":671343,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T05:17:00.000Z","msg":"攬住自己唯一既至愛跳橋 rip"},{"pid":"592af8dfab099f95cc79e18aaa7a33efb10a6e22","tid":671343,"uid":37463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T05:58:35.000Z","msg":"家人同住於<span style=\"color: red;\">沙田水泉澳邨</span>。據悉，黃父從事<span style=\"color: red;\">洗衣業生意</span>，他近年到<span style=\"color: red;\">父親的洗衣工場</span>幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n資產？入息？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162f9a4d1514edd7a961302b27037599b0226154","tid":671343,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:11:26.000Z","msg":"沿水影響？"}]}